data.description: You most certainly will not have time to think twice about this attractive and well cared for 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom one level, nearly full brick home on almost 2 acres! The undeniably comfortable and smartly designed interior features an inviting living room with updated luxury plank flooring, a fully updated kitchen with granite countertops and subway tile backsplash, breakfast nook, split bedroom plan with a large primary suite that has plenty of closet space, and large ensuite with walk-in shower, soaking tub, large vanity. This dwelling also boasts a large sunroom overlooking the private back lawn. Off the rear doors will lead you to the private back yard that has a patio area, pergola, beautiful landscaping and tons of fruit trees. Uniquely designed, this home is constructed of steal beams. This rare rural find is an absolute gem!
